snippet.title: WizardChess - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
WizardChess is OUT NOW ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1274210/WizardChess

What if chess was invented by silly cosmic wizards? WizardChess is a turnbased roguelite where all the pieces have insane abilities that came to us in a shamanic vision. Fight chaotic-yet-tactical encounters with magic powers out of a fever dream! Defeat the FaeQueen and Claim Your Wish!
